high_descs: Turn right and cross the room then hang a left and walk forward, turn left right before the doorway to face the little black end table next to the couch
Open the drawer that's on the end table and pick up the keys that are inside then close the drawer
Head across the room to the tall floor lamp that is past the couch
anns.task_desc: Examine a set of keys under a tall lamp

high_descs: Turn to the right and move across the room. Turn left and face the small black table on the left.
Open the drawer and take out the keys. Shut the door.
Carry the keys and to the left and then turn right. Face the tall lamp to the right, in the corner.
Hold up the keys and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp while holding keys.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to the armchair in the corner, then turn left and walk forward to the small black table to the right of the green sofa.
Take out the key chain from the drawer of the table and close the drawer.
Walk across the room, past the green sofa to the right to the tall lamp in the corner to the left of the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Examine a key chain by the light of a floor lamp.
